+
+The strongest pattern was feature_041. Each 1-unit increase in feature_041 was associated with +${rnd(f041.beta)} months of PFS (${ptxt(f041.p)}), and the top quartile had ${rnd(f041q.diff)} months longer PFS than the bottom quartile. This association was monotonic and remained the dominant effect.
